# Ignore everything...
*

# other than specific top-level files...
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md
!RendScroll.exe
!launcher.py
!index.html
!update_manifest.json
# package.json declares the jsdom dev-dependency used by the DOM-render tests
# (node --test). node_modules / package-lock.json stay ignored.
!package.json

# and Source folders...
!src/
!src/**
!test/
!test/**
!Documentation/
!Documentation/**

# and campaign folders...
# Campaigns/ holds multi-campaign content (each a self-contained folder). The
# structure is committed via .gitkeep; the campaign .md/asset files are local
# user content (ignored by the `*` rule above).
!Campaigns/
!Campaigns/.gitkeep
!images/
!images/.gitkeep
!audio/
!audio/.gitkeep
# reusable reference libraries (Items, Enemies, …) — folder structure is committed;
# the library .md files themselves are local user content (ignored).
!Items/
!Items/.gitkeep
!Enemies/
!Enemies/.gitkeep

# but still ignore compiled Python files
*.pyc
Documentation/Tutorials/**